== Testing Instructions

**Browser mode** (default - uses CDN):
```
doclang build maps_offline_test.slidelang --render-mode=browser
```

**Offline assets** (PNG files saved to assets/):
```
doclang build maps_offline_test.slidelang --render-mode=offline-assets
```

**Offline inline** (Base64 embedded):
```
doclang build maps_offline_test.slidelang --render-mode=offline-inline
```

---

== Expected Results

- **Browser mode**: Interactive Leaflet maps with zoom/pan
- **Offline assets**: Static PNG images in `output/maps_offline_test.html/assets/`
- **Offline inline**: Static PNG images embedded as Base64

All modes should show:
- Correct map tiles (world/city/region)
- All markers visible
- Labels readable
- Proper zoom levels
- Correct colors (blue/red/green/orange)
